# Databricks Delta Live Tables – Bronze Ingestion

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates a Delta Live Tables (DLT) Bronze ingestion pipeline using
Databricks Auto Loader and Unity Catalog volumes.

## Architecture
Source (JSON Files)
→ Auto Loader
→ Bronze DLT Tables
→ Unity Catalog (raw.transactions)

## Technologies Used
- Azure Databricks
- Delta Live Tables (DLT)
- Unity Catalog
- Auto Loader
- PySpark

## Bronze Tables
- orders_bronze
- payments_bronze

## How to Run
1. Create DLT pipeline in Databricks
2. Attach `bronze_ingestion_dlt.py`
3. Set catalog = raw, schema = transactions
4. Run pipeline

## Validation
Validation queries are available in `sql/validation_queries.sql`

## Screenshots
Screenshots proving pipeline execution are available in `/screenshots`
